stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> BOOT_BLOCKED
  BOOT_BLOCKED --> DISCOVERING_FILES: acquire recovery gate
  DISCOVERING_FILES --> DOUBLEWRITE_REPAIRING: lifecycle S latch per tablespace
  DOUBLEWRITE_REPAIRING --> REDO_REPLAYING: release doublewrite file locks
  REDO_REPLAYING --> DDL_RECOVERING: redo complete
  DDL_RECOVERING --> TRX_ROLLBACKING: dictionary stable
  TRX_ROLLBACKING --> PURGE_RESUMING: active rollback complete
  PURGE_RESUMING --> WORKERS_STARTING: purge view initialized
  WORKERS_STARTING --> USER_TRAFFIC_OPEN: page cleaner and checkpoint workers ready
  USER_TRAFFIC_OPEN --> [*]

  DISCOVERING_FILES --> FAILED: file header or redo control error
  DOUBLEWRITE_REPAIRING --> FAILED: unrecoverable torn page
  REDO_REPLAYING --> FAILED: corrupt required redo
  DDL_RECOVERING --> FAILED: unrecoverable DDL log
  TRX_ROLLBACKING --> FAILED: rollback failure
  FAILED --> [*]
